<section id="dspCountTagsByItem">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>count tags</primary>

      <secondary>by item</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>items</primary>

      <secondary>count tags for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Count Tags by Item</title>

  <para>To view a display of Count Tags by item, select the "Count Tags by
  Item" option. The following screen will appear:</para>

  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/dspCountTagsByItem.png" />
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Count Tags by Item</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>

  <para>When displaying Count Tags by item, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Number</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the item number of the item Count Tags you want to view.
        The lookup feature located to the right of the field leads to a
        searchable list of make and buy items.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>UOM</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Inventory unit of measure.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry role="standard">
      <term>All Sites</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display Count Tags for all sites.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry role="standard">
      <term>Selected</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Specify site whose Count Tags you want to display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Start Date</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Count Tags entered on and after this date will be
        displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>End Date</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Count Tags entered on and before this date will be
        displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Unposted Count Tags</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display unposted Count Tags.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Count Tags</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists Count Tags by item, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

</section>
